info.author: Advanced Software Engineering Ltd
info.description:
Professional chart and graph library. Unique layering architecture enables you 
to synthesize the charts you want using standard chart layers.  Support all 
major chart types, including meters and guages. Charts are interactive, 
supporting tool tips, clickable chart objects, and "drag to zoom" and "drag to 
scroll" features. AJAX enabled. Easy to use and with comprehensive 
documentation.
